## Summary

In this exercise, you validated the hardened end state of the Azure AI application by confirming the deployed architecture, reviewing App Service access restrictions, checking Storage account data protection settings, and using Defender for Cloud and Microsoft Purview as evidence of security posture and governance readiness. This capstone demonstrates that the application is not only deployed successfully, but also secured and governable across its lifecycle.
